        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>TriggerUpdateFlag</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para><verbatim>                Update the associated accumulator from
</verbatim> the FREQUENCY registers: </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>0 = NO_UPDATE: Do not update</para></listitem><listitem><para>1 = IMMEDIATE_UPDATE: Apply an immediate update</para></listitem><listitem><para>2 = TRIGGER_UPDATE: Apply an update on the next CC_UPDATE trigger. Note: This flag acts as a command and is self-clearing. Once the update condition is met, the value automatically reverts to 0 (NO_UPDATE), which will be reflected in subsequent XDfeMix_GetCurrentCCCfg calls. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
